This is some helpers for working with Gtk2 widgets and stuff.

* Gtk2::Ex::WidgetBits -- misc funcs

* Gtk2::Ex::GdkBits -- misc funcs

* Gtk2::Ex::KeySnooper -- oop style key snooper hook

* Gtk2::Ex::SyncCall -- callback after server sync


The only prerequisite is Gtk2-Perl.  The WidgetBits home page is

    http://www.geocities.com/user42_kevin/gtk2-ex-widgetbits/index.html

Bug reports to the author at user42@zip.com.au please.
